-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

262
00:17:44,485 --> 00:17:45,885
What's wrong with him?

263
00:17:45,965 --> 00:17:47,045
Why isn't he singing?

264
00:17:50,925 --> 00:17:52,325
What's going on?

265
00:17:53,205 --> 00:17:55,045
-Are you in charge of the microphones?
-Yes.

266
00:17:55,125 --> 00:17:57,365
-Do you know where you put them?
-Yes, they're backstage.

267
00:17:57,445 --> 00:17:58,805
I know where they are. I'll get them.

268
00:17:58,885 --> 00:18:01,405
You better find them,
or they'll wreck the stage!

269
00:18:05,845 --> 00:18:07,125
What the hell happened?

270
00:18:07,565 --> 00:18:08,685
Goodness.

271
00:18:12,205 --> 00:18:13,685
I definitely put it here.

272
00:18:16,165 --> 00:18:17,005
Who's there?

273
00:18:21,525 --> 00:18:22,365
Stop!

274
00:18:24,125 --> 00:18:26,205
What are you doing backstage?

275
00:18:26,285 --> 00:18:27,165
I...

276
00:18:28,565 --> 00:18:30,125
I didn't take the microphones!

277
00:18:38,285 --> 00:18:39,605
Dalei!

278
00:18:42,565 --> 00:18:44,125
I went to take the microphones.

279
00:18:44,205 --> 00:18:45,925
Suddenly, a heroine appeared.

280
00:18:46,965 --> 00:18:48,285
Then I lost the microphones.

281
00:18:48,365 --> 00:18:50,765
-A heroine?
-Yes.

282
00:18:54,885 --> 00:18:56,605
-I'm sorry!
-Hey, what are you doing?

283
00:18:56,845 --> 00:18:57,805
Wait.

284
00:18:58,725 --> 00:18:59,805
Isn't that Qingqing?

285
00:19:03,645 --> 00:19:05,125
Where is the mic stand?

286
00:19:05,205 --> 00:19:06,045
Mic stand?

287
00:19:09,325 --> 00:19:10,165
It's me.

288
00:19:10,685 --> 00:19:11,725
I'll be the mic stand.

289
00:19:13,085 --> 00:19:14,685
You may start now.

290
00:19:25,845 --> 00:19:29,325
I've never promoted this song before.

291
00:19:31,525 --> 00:19:32,885
I'd like to dedicate it

292
00:19:32,965 --> 00:19:35,325
to a special,

293
00:19:36,125 --> 00:19:37,325
special person.

294
00:19:38,125 --> 00:19:39,605
I hope you'll like it.

295
00:19:41,205 --> 00:19:42,165
You are all useless!

296
00:19:50,285 --> 00:19:54,565
As the ocean falls into deep silence

297
00:19:57,405 --> 00:20:00,885
The wind blows to the bottom of my heart

298
00:20:02,005 --> 00:20:05,165
Looking at you from a distance
In my memories

299
00:20:05,245 --> 00:20:08,885
A familiar figure I see from behind

300
00:20:09,205 --> 00:20:11,445
I didn't manage

301
00:20:12,765 --> 00:20:15,205
To grab your hand

302
00:20:19,285 --> 00:20:23,685
If I ever see you again

303
00:20:26,605 --> 00:20:30,725
Even if just to say hello

304
00:20:30,805 --> 00:20:34,485
Time will fish me out of the sea

305
00:20:34,565 --> 00:20:38,245
While my heart is left adrift

306
00:20:38,325 --> 00:20:40,045
All that's left

307
00:20:40,525 --> 00:20:42,765
Is a chill in the air

308
00:20:42,845 --> 00:20:47,365
To sigh with me

309
00:20:50,125 --> 00:20:53,045
I took off my hand

310
00:20:53,845 --> 00:20:56,205
And let you go

311
00:20:57,565 --> 00:21:03,685
I couldn't pretend that you weren't here

312
00:21:04,725 --> 00:21:07,765
Ever since then,

313
00:21:08,365 --> 00:21:11,285
I'm being punished

314
00:21:11,845 --> 00:21:17,045
When breathing hurts without you

315
00:21:17,965 --> 00:21:19,285
He's singing so well!

316
00:21:19,365 --> 00:21:22,245
I took off my hand

317
00:21:22,805 --> 00:21:25,645
And let you go

318
00:21:26,325 --> 00:21:33,325
I couldn't pretend that you weren't here

319
00:21:33,765 --> 00:21:36,885
Ever since then

320
00:21:37,365 --> 00:21:40,565
I'm being punished

321
00:21:41,125 --> 00:21:47,165
When breathing hurts without you

322
00:21:48,325 --> 00:21:52,565
When breathing hurts

323
00:21:54,245 --> 00:21:56,525
Without you

324
00:22:32,365 --> 00:22:34,245
Why didn't you follow our plan?

325
00:22:34,325 --> 00:22:36,045
You insisted on singing "Breath"!

326
00:22:37,325 --> 00:22:38,205
Never mind.

327
00:22:38,285 --> 00:22:40,285
Mei, take him to rest.

328
00:22:42,125 --> 00:22:43,325
Damn it.

329
00:22:49,765 --> 00:22:52,445
Hey! Fangfang, listen up--

330
00:23:10,765 --> 00:23:11,605
Done.

331
00:23:18,245 --> 00:23:19,085
Qingqing.

332
00:23:21,085 --> 00:23:22,205
What is it?

333
00:23:22,885 --> 00:23:24,125
I...

334
00:23:26,525 --> 00:23:27,685
I forgot.

335
00:23:38,325 --> 00:23:40,925
Please turn to page 32.

336
00:23:41,325 --> 00:23:45,365
We will continue to talk
about the inscribed circle of triangle

337
00:23:45,445 --> 00:23:48,965
and find the radius r
of the inscribed circle

338
00:23:49,045 --> 00:23:51,365
based on the conditional angles
A, I and B.

339
00:23:51,925 --> 00:23:55,365
We've discussed this diagram before,
so it's a common question...

340
00:23:55,445 --> 00:23:57,685
Hey, what happened to your hand?

341
00:23:59,045 --> 00:24:01,005
It's nothing, it's just a scratch.

342
00:24:20,445 --> 00:24:21,885
What's that?

343
00:24:23,765 --> 00:24:24,965
A band-aid?

344
00:24:25,725 --> 00:24:26,605
Yes.

345
00:24:27,165 --> 00:24:28,045
For me?

346
00:24:28,605 --> 00:24:29,445
Yes.

347
00:24:40,165 --> 00:24:41,125
Hey.

348
00:24:42,165 --> 00:24:44,485
Is this a caricature of you?

349
00:24:45,165 --> 00:24:46,965
It looks ugly.

350
00:24:47,605 --> 00:24:50,445
-Hey. Give it back if you don't want it.
-I want it.

351
00:24:52,605 --> 00:24:54,645
Who on earth would take back

352
00:24:54,725 --> 00:24:56,445
what they just gave to someone?

353
00:24:57,485 --> 00:25:01,605
Besides, I hurt my hands because of you.

354
00:25:01,685 --> 00:25:04,885
So there's nothing peculiar
about sticking your head on it.

355
00:25:26,725 --> 00:25:28,685
Are you humming my song from yesterday?

356
00:25:28,965 --> 00:25:30,125
You picked it up so fast.

357
00:25:36,645 --> 00:25:40,045
Who told you to keep the melody so simple?

358
00:25:40,805 --> 00:25:42,205
Of course I'd pick it up fast.

359
00:25:54,045 --> 00:25:56,125
Is something wrong with me?

360
00:25:57,125 --> 00:25:59,325
It's 120 beats per minute?

361
00:26:04,045 --> 00:26:04,885
Qingqing.

362
00:26:04,965 --> 00:26:06,125
What's wrong?

363
00:26:06,205 --> 00:26:09,085
I don't know what's going on.

364
00:26:09,365 --> 00:26:12,365
My heart is beating strangely lately.

365
00:26:12,805 --> 00:26:15,445
Sometimes, it throbs so fast.

366
00:26:15,685 --> 00:26:17,885
Isn't there anyone you like?

367
00:26:19,165 --> 00:26:20,005
Fangfang.

368
00:26:20,085 --> 00:26:21,885
You have got to be kidding me.

369
00:26:22,085 --> 00:26:24,725
I'm Chen Qingqing. Who do I like?

370
00:26:26,685 --> 00:26:27,725
I'm about to go out.

371
00:26:27,805 --> 00:26:29,165
Do you want me to buy something?

372
00:26:29,845 --> 00:26:31,085
No, thanks.

373
00:26:46,205 --> 00:26:48,485
He's so handsome.

374
00:27:07,205 --> 00:27:08,045
Situ Feng!

375
00:27:13,365 --> 00:27:14,605
The comic has got a new update.

376
00:27:14,965 --> 00:27:17,245
Let's see how badly
he disses His Highness this time.

377
00:27:18,725 --> 00:27:19,765
He says,

378
00:27:19,845 --> 00:27:21,885
"His Highness sang a song of resentment."

379
00:27:22,445 --> 00:27:25,605
And the lyrics sounds a lot like "Breath."

380
00:27:25,685 --> 00:27:29,005
How about we upload
a recording of that song

381
00:27:29,205 --> 00:27:31,245
-and see what the fans think?
-Yeah.

382
00:27:34,165 --> 00:27:37,365
SITU FENG NEW SONG
"BREATH" IS SO PLEASANT.

383
00:27:44,205 --> 00:27:46,045
Since it's so well-received...

384
00:27:46,125 --> 00:27:49,205
We'll include "Breath"
into your upcoming album.

385
00:27:49,285 --> 00:27:50,405
Look at yourself.

386
00:27:50,485 --> 00:27:53,365
Do you really think you could be
in Situ Feng's music video?

387
00:27:53,445 --> 00:27:55,605
This is Situ Feng's music video?

388
00:27:55,685 --> 00:27:59,365
Are you not aware that they're looking
for someone with outstanding qualities?

389
00:27:59,445 --> 00:28:01,285
Qualities?

390
00:28:01,365 --> 00:28:02,965
I have them.

391
00:28:04,325 --> 00:28:07,165
So what if you've got so many supporters?

392
00:28:07,245 --> 00:28:10,125
You can't even eat a bar of chocolate.

393
00:28:10,205 --> 00:28:12,005
If you help me run errands...

394
00:28:12,085 --> 00:28:15,485
You could eat plenty of snacks.
Nobody would notice.

395
